snippet.title: Labyrinth - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Enter the maze with nothing but a semi-useful mini-map. Make your way through four different maze sizes while racing against the clock for the pride of becoming Mazelord. It will not be easy with near misses causing you to cringe for more.

Music: http://www.bensound.com/royalty-free-music
